\insrsid13787376  Overview}}}{\insrsid13787376  Peak Works for Windows Program Overview
\par }\pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid13787376 The }{\b\insrsid13787376 Peak Works for Windows }{\insrsid13787376 
program controls the entire operation of the Gas Chromatograph, including setting temperatures, switching fluidics and alarm valves, data acquisition, processing, displaying, storing, and supplying the analog and digital outputs to other equipments}{
\fs20\insrsid13787376 .    
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\sl-240\slmult1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\insrsid13787376 \page }{\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 *{\footnote \pard\plain 
\s16\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 *}{\insrsid13787376  Stand_alone}}}{\insrsid13787376  }{
\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 ${\footnote \pard\plain \s16\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 $}{\insrsid13787376 
 WPEAK Computing Integrator Overview}}}{\insrsid13787376  }{\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 #{\footnote \pard\plain \s16\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 
\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 #}{\insrsid13787376  Overview}}}{\insrsid13787376  }{\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 K{\footnote \pard\plain 
\s16\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 K}{\insrsid13787376  Overview}}}{\insrsid13787376  }{\b\cf2\insrsid13787376 
WPEAK Computing Integrator Overview
\par }\pard\plain \s16\ql \li0\ri0\sl-240\slmult1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid13787376 
\par }\pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\sl-240\slmult1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid13787376 The }{\b\insrsid13787376 WPEAK Computing Integrator}{
\insrsid13787376  is a variant of the }{\b\insrsid13787376 Peak Works for Windows}{\insrsid13787376  program developed by the HNU Systems / PID Analyzers, together with an interface device to receive 
analog data from and to communicate with a gas chromatograph. This variant of the program can be installed in a desktop or a laptop computer, and analog signals from any gas chromatograph can be sent to the analog inputs of the }{\b\insrsid13787376 
Integrator}{\insrsid13787376 . There are also several digital input and output lines at the }{\b\insrsid13787376 Integrator}{\insrsid13787376  that allow a handshaking between the }{\b\insrsid13787376 Integrator}{\insrsid13787376 
 and the Gas Chromatograph.  The }{\b\insrsid13787376 WPEAK Computing Integrator}{\insrsid13787376  performs data acquisition, processing, displaying, and storing the results to the hard drive of the PC. 
\par \page }{\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 ${\footnote \pard\plain \s16\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 $}{
\insrsid13787376  Method Overview}}}{\insrsid13787376  }{\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 #{\footnote \pard\plain \s16\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 
\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 #}{\insrsid13787376  MethodOverview}}}{\insrsid13787376  }{\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 K{\footnote \pard\plain 
\s16\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs15\fs18\up6\insrsid13787376 K}{\insrsid13787376  Method Overview; Method: Overview}}}{\insrsid13787376  }
{\b\cf2\insrsid13787376 Method Overview}{\insrsid13787376 
\par Method developed for the chromatograph to analyze gas samples includes many parameters of the process, such as the specific task time sequences, tempe
ratures in working zones, names and chromatographic parameters of the gas or liquid to be analyzed, calibration standards, alarm levels for different components, types of detectors installed, parameters of the data acquisition, processing, analyzing, and 
outputting the results to other electronic equipment. 
\par    The Method for a particular application is set up through several }{\b\insrsid13787376 Method Menu}{\insrsid13787376  items:
\par }{\b\insrsid13787376 Method|Edit}{\insrsid13787376  item opens the }{\uldb\insrsid13787376 Method Dialog Box}{\v\insrsid13787376 ID_METHODDIALOG}{\insrsid13787376 
 to set the time schedule of the GC operations, Oven and Detector temperatures, points to be analyzed and to enable/disable alarms in those points. 
\par }{\b\insrsid13787376 Method|Detector}{\insrsid13787376  item opens the }{\uldb\insrsid13787376 Detector Dialog Box}{\v\insrsid13787376 ID_DETECTORDIALOG}{\insrsid13787376 
 so the user can enable/disable the particular detector, select the detector type, select the data acquisition parameters and the peak detection algorithm, and set the 4-20 mA analog output range.
\par }{\b\insrsid13787376 Method|Components}{\insrsid13787376  item opens the }{\uldb\insrsid13787376 Components Dialog Box}{\v\insrsid13787376 ID_COMPONENTSDIALOG}{\insrsid13787376 
 where the user can input the names, retention times, and other chromatographic parameters of the gas or liquid to be analyzed.
\par }{\b\insrsid13787376 Method|Standards}{\insrsid13787376  item opens the }{\uldb\insrsid13787376 Standards Dialog Box}{\v\uldb\insrsid13787376 ID_STANDARDSDIALOG}{\insrsid13787376  where the user inputs the concentration of 
the Standards (up to four) to be used for calibrating the instrument. 
\par }{\b\insrsid13787376 Method|Save}{\insrsid13787376  item saves all the parameters into the opened JOB file. It is possible to save different Methods into several JOB files; on start of the WPEAK program, the particular Method
 can be loaded automatically if one places the corresponding JOB file name into the \'93Load File\'94 edit box in the }{\uldb\insrsid13787376 Preferences Dialog Box}{\v\insrsid13787376 ID_PREFERENCESDIALOG}{\insrsid13787376  that can be opened with the }{
\b\insrsid13787376 Options|Preferences}{\insrsid13787376  menu item.       
\par }\pard\plain \s16\ql \li0\ri0\sl-240\slmult1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid13787376     
