This item works only in the graph Window, not in the table Window. First select (click on) the graph Window. The Axis item is used to expand the sensitivity (Y-axis) and select the time coordinates (X-axis). To use
 this, click on the (x) in the Y- or X-axis, change the coordinates, then, the entire chromatogram is displayed with the new coordinates.
\par }\pard\plain \s1\ql \li0\ri0\sb280\sa120\sl-320\slmult0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\fs24\cf2\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid13787376 \page }{
