 only acquires, processes, and displays data from the gas chromatograph and do
es not set the process parameters to the GC. However, it can control the mode of data acquisition and initiate the GC to start a run. Fill in edit boxes and check boxes for the following parameters:
\par a. The }{\b\insrsid13787376 Analysis Time,}{\insrsid13787376  in a format of mm:ss or hh:mm:ss, c
an be set up to 2 hours.  If the run duration in the GC is set for longer time than the analysis time in this edit box, the data acquisition will stop after the Analysis Time passes from the start of the run. In case the run at the GC finishes before the 
Analysis Time elapses, the analysis will stop on receiving the signal \'93Run Finished\'94 from the GC. 
\par b. In }{\b\insrsid13787376 Misc. Table}{\insrsid13787376 : 
