\par \tab }{\b\insrsid13787376 Calibration Cycle }{\insrsid13787376 - time interval between automatic calibrations, 0 to 24 hours. If it is set to 0, no calibration run will be forced.
\par \tab }{\b\insrsid13787376 Repeat Cycle  }{\insrsid13787376 - the period for the system to fulfill a single scan through all the active points.  
\par }\pard \ql \fi-270\li270\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin270\itap0 {\insrsid13787376 
