\par Chose points you want to be active. You can enable/disable Low and/or High alarms in each of the active points.  
\par }\pard\plain \s16\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid13787376 
