\par }\pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid13787376 This menu item brings }{\uldb\insrsid13787376 Run Modes Dialog Box}{
\insrsid13787376 .
\par }{\v\insrsid13787376 ID_RUNMODEDIALOG}{\insrsid13787376 Chose the }{\b\insrsid13787376 Run Mode }{\insrsid13787376 as Manual, Continuous, Repeat, or Remote. (Some modes are disabled for particular applications of the Peak Works):
\par \tab - }{\b\insrsid13787376 Manual}{\insrsid13787376  Run Mode produces a single run at the selected point;
\par \tab - }{\b\insrsid13787376 Continuous}{\insrsid13787376 
 Run Mode results in the continuous scan through all active points; the analysis data is saved in the [MMDDYY.job] and [MMDDYY.run] files, new files to be automatically opened around a midnight with the file names corresponding to the new date. 
\par }\pard \ql \li720\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin720\itap0 {\b\insrsid13787376 - Repeat}{\insrsid13787376 
 Run Mode fulfils a single scan through all active points, and repeats the scan with a period set by the Repeat Time edit box in the }{\uldb\insrsid13787376 Method Dialog Box}{\v\insrsid13787376 ID_METHODDIALOG}{\uldb\insrsid13787376 .
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\insrsid13787376 . \tab - }{\b\insrsid13787376 Remote}{\insrsid13787376  Run Mode fulfils a single run on the external command (dry contact
 closure at the dedicated digital input of the GC).
\par The Run can be saved manually (only if Manual Run Mode is selected), automatically, or on alarm (check the corresponding }{\b\insrsid13787376 Save Run }{\insrsid13787376 Mode}{\b\insrsid13787376  }{\insrsid13787376 button).  
\par }{\fs20\insrsid13787376 
\par }\pard\plain \s1\ql \li0\ri0\sb280\sa120\sl-320\slmult0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\fs24\cf2\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid13787376 \page }{
