\b0\insrsid13787376  }{\insrsid13787376 Shift Modes Dialog Box}{\b0\insrsid13787376 
\par }\pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid13787376 
This feature is available only for the Multi-Point Process Chromatographs GC501b and GC501c.
\par This menu item sets the procedures of saving and printing shift reports.
\par }{\v\insrsid13787376 ID_RUNMODEDIALOG}{\insrsid13787376 Chose the }{\b\insrsid13787376 Save Report }{\insrsid13787376 Mode as Manual, Auto, or On Alarm: 
\par }\pard \ql \fi-810\li810\ri0\widctlpar\tx720\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin810\itap0 {\insrsid13787376 \tab - }{\b\insrsid13787376 Manual}{\insrsid13787376 
 Save Report Mode. With this selection, go to File/SaveReport menu and save the report as a Rich Text Format file (*.rtf) or Text file (*.txt). Both formats are supported by the WordPad editor available in the GC. 
\par \tab - }{\b\insrsid13787376 Auto}{\insrsid13787376  Save Report Mode saves the shift report automatically in the end of each shift in the Continuous Run Mode.
\par }\pard \ql \fi-720\li720\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin720\itap0 {\insrsid13787376 \tab - }{\b\insrsid13787376 On Alarm }{\insrsid13787376 
Save Report Mode saves the shift report each time any alarm occurs in the run AND in the end of the shift (in the }{\b\insrsid13787376 Continuous Run Mode}{\insrsid13787376 ). 
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\insrsid13787376 Chose the }{\b\insrsid13787376 Print Report Mode}{\insrsid13787376  as }{\b\insrsid13787376 Manual}{\insrsid13787376 , }{\b\insrsid13787376 Auto
}{\insrsid13787376 , or }{\b\insrsid13787376 On Alarm}{\insrsid13787376 :
\par }\pard \ql \fi-810\li810\ri0\widctlpar\tx720\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin810\itap0 {\insrsid13787376 \tab - }{\b\insrsid13787376 Manual}{\insrsid13787376 
 Print Report Mode. With this selection, in order to print the Shift Report, open the Window/Summary for the selected detector and press the Print icon \{bmc print.bmp\}at the Toolbar.
\par \tab - }{\b\insrsid13787376 Auto}{\insrsid13787376  Print Report Mode. The Shift Report is printed automatically in the end of each shift in the Continuous Run Mode.
\par \tab - }{\b\insrsid13787376 On Alarm }{\insrsid13787376 Print Report Mode. The Shift Report is printed each time any alarm occurs in the run AND in the end of the shift (in the }{\b\insrsid13787376 Continuous Run Mode}{\insrsid13787376 ). 
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\fs20\insrsid13787376 \page }{\cs15\fs18\cf1\up6\insrsid13787376 *{\footnote \pard\plain 
