\par When an existing job is loaded}{\b\insrsid13787376 , }{\insrsid13787376 go to the select run menu item and click on the run, which is to be displayed in the graph Window. The click on the }{\b\insrsid13787376 Integrate}{\insrsid13787376 
 button, and the results will be displayed in another Window (Table). You can also use the icons: click on the folder and the Runs will be displayed; click on the chromatogram and the chromatograms will be integrated.
