With the currently selected run having been integrated, this menu item is enabled. When it is clicked on, the }{\uldb\insrsid13787376 Select Run(s) from List Dialog Box}{\insrsid13787376 
 pops up, and the calibration results from the current run can be saved into the runs selected from the list. After that, each of those runs can be selected with the Run|Select Run menu item and re-integrated using this new calibration data.
