\v\fs20\uldb\insrsid13787376 ID_RUNMODEDIALOG}{\fs20\insrsid13787376  }{\insrsid13787376 that allows selecting a }{\b\insrsid13787376 Run Mode}{\insrsid13787376  (Manual, Continuous, Repeat, or Remote) and a }{\b\insrsid13787376 Save Run Mode}{
\insrsid13787376  (Manual, Auto, or On Alarm).
\par }{\b\insrsid13787376 Run Mode}{\insrsid13787376  options:
\par }\pard \ql \fi720\li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\insrsid13787376 Manual}{\insrsid13787376  \endash  the GC makes a single run at the current point. 
\par }\pard \ql \li720\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin720\itap0 {\b\insrsid13787376 Continuous}{\insrsid13787376  \endash  the GC continuously scans all the points enabled in the }{\uldb\insrsid13787376 
Points & Alarms Dialog Box}{\v\dbch\af11\insrsid13787376 \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 ID_POINTSDIALOG}{\insrsid13787376 . 
\par }{\b\insrsid13787376 Repeat }{\insrsid13787376 \endash  the GC repeats a single scan through all the points enabled in the }{\uldb\insrsid13787376 Points & Alarms Dialog Box}{\v\dbch\af11\insrsid13787376 \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 ID_POINTSDIALOG}{
\insrsid13787376  with a period set as the }{\b\insrsid13787376 Repeat Cycle}{\insrsid13787376  in the }{\uldb\insrsid13787376 Method Dialog Box}{\v\insrsid13787376 ID_METHODDIALOG}{\insrsid13787376 .  
\par }{\b\insrsid13787376 Remote }{\insrsid13787376 \endash  the GC waits for a }{\b\insrsid13787376 Remote Start}{\insrsid13787376  command (dry contact closure at the terminal) and makes a single run at t
he current point on receiving the command. This mode is optional and available not in all the GCs.
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\insrsid13787376 Save Run Mode }{\insrsid13787376 options:
